# Memory Bank

At the start of every task, read all files in `memory-bank/` in order. This is your only link to previous work.

**Files:** projectbrief.md → productContext.md → systemPatterns.md → techContext.md → activeContext.md → progress.md → journal.md

**Priority:** Memory Bank supersedes other rules, skills, and agents when in conflict.

**Update when:** After significant changes; when user says "update memory bank"; when context needs clarification. Focus on activeContext.md and progress.md. When user says "update memory bank", review ALL files.

**MCP:** Cloudflare, GitHub, Statsig – use when relevant.
